precis:
Enactment of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES MINING DISTRICT AND NUNAVUT MINING
DISTRICT ORDER - which (a) divides the territorial lands in the Northwest
Territories and in Nunavut into two mining districts, and (b) repeals the
Northwest Territories Mining Districts Order made in 1992.
